import pandas as pd
from datetime import datetime, timedelta

def format(path):
    # Read the CSV file
    df = pd.read_csv(path)
    
    # Convert the 4th column (index 3) to datetime and subtract 3 hours
    df.iloc[:, 3] = pd.to_datetime(df.iloc[:, 3]) - timedelta(hours=3)
    
    # Save to Excel file
    df.to_excel('/workspace/audit-export.xlsx', index=False)

if __name__ == '__main__':
    import sys
    if len(sys.argv) > 1:
        format(sys.argv[1])
    else:
        print("Please provide a path to the CSV file")
